measurements.description: Thirty-six flowers and nine buds on four arching to pendulous inflorescences to 73cm length; dorsal sepal hooded, lanceolate, yellow spotted burgundy; lateral sepals lanceolate, light yellow, densely spotted burgundy, diffussed burgundy distally; petals lanceolate, yellow spotted and blotched burgundy; lip yellow, blotched burgundy; column yellow overlaid rose, anther cap cream; substance average; texture matte.
